    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Dreadway》是一款在线合作生存恐怖游戏，包含制作、近距离语音聊天、可怕的怪物，以及以声音驱动的互动。你和最多三位朋友穿梭于末日后的世界，收集破烂，制作求生装置，并通过语音聊天与游戏互动。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>合作撤离恐怖——你的声音就是钥匙。</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/5dda30a2796ea63eca8255b69b4c2538.poster.avif?t=1769872973\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/5dda30a2796ea63eca8255b69b4c2538.webm?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/5dda30a2796ea63eca8255b69b4c2538.mp4?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>☢☢☢  你的声音就是钥匙  ☢☢☢</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用语音聊天来打开密码锁和门。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/6354b19585d40199400adcc621050862.poster.avif?t=1769872973\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/6354b19585d40199400adcc621050862.webm?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/6354b19585d40199400adcc621050862.mp4?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/070aedf96398cd88f5bfa8846a065e04.poster.avif?t=1769872973\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/070aedf96398cd88f5bfa8846a065e04.webm?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/070aedf96398cd88f5bfa8846a065e04.mp4?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>☢☢☢  大喊才能活下去  ☢☢☢</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怪物会对你做出反应。喊出暗号把它们吓跑…</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/a997a52e48145b2902da1049357e44f2.poster.avif?t=1769872973\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/a997a52e48145b2902da1049357e44f2.webm?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/a997a52e48145b2902da1049357e44f2.mp4?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>☢☢☢  踢你的朋友  ☢☢☢</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踢队友来打断、拯救、整蛊，或把他们推进麻烦里。合作混乱。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/bd85946d55a2bd8f70035f0ac5f7eb20.poster.avif?t=1769872973\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/bd85946d55a2bd8f70035f0ac5f7eb20.webm?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/bd85946d55a2bd8f70035f0ac5f7eb20.mp4?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>☢☢☢  喂饱列车  ☢☢☢</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >列车一直需要燃料。把你收集到的一切烧掉，让它继续前进。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/1a9a015b3d407b49fdec3aa150470290.poster.avif?t=1769872973\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/1a9a015b3d407b49fdec3aa150470290.webm?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/1a9a015b3d407b49fdec3aa150470290.mp4?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>☢☢☢  一起玩得开心  ☢☢☢</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胡闹、即兴——每一次出击都是你和朋友的独特故事。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/e5b9245283ffdf9fd99ccf811d3a8674.poster.avif?t=1769872973\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/e5b9245283ffdf9fd99ccf811d3a8674.webm?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/e5b9245283ffdf9fd99ccf811d3a8674.mp4?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>☢☢☢  避开陷阱  ☢☢☢</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持专注，注意脚下——一次失误就可能毁掉整趟外出。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/0c5ffc33fe7225b68dff5e3af8279df4.poster.avif?t=1769872973\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/0c5ffc33fe7225b68dff5e3af8279df4.webm?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/0c5ffc33fe7225b68dff5e3af8279df4.mp4?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>☢☢☢  收集资源  ☢☢☢</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集破烂和重要资源——每件物品都可能救你…也可能害你。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/c614bb2b93a40018ab14288c4d07e979.poster.avif?t=1769872973\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/c614bb2b93a40018ab14288c4d07e979.webm?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/c614bb2b93a40018ab14288c4d07e979.mp4?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>☢☢☢  制作物品  ☢☢☢</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你找到的任何东西制作工具和装置。升级你的角色。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/4482c4b4be4d12c4ea9253ef5f4f048a.poster.avif?t=1769872973\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/4482c4b4be4d12c4ea9253ef5f4f048a.webm?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215820/extras/4482c4b4be4d12c4ea9253ef5f4f048a.mp4?t=1769872973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在线合作最多 4 人<br></li><li>地堡中的合作解谜<br></li><li>具有独特行为的怪物<br></li><li>近距离语音聊天——可在距离内交谈<br></li><li>语音玩法：密码锁、门<br></li><li>怪物能听见你——你的声音可能暴露位置<br></li><li>喊出暗号来吓跑怪物<br></li><li>利用找到的破烂制作：工具、装置、生存装备<br></li><li>角色升级<br></li><li>用踢击制造混乱与破坏<br></li><li>需要喂燃料的列车<br></li><li>陷阱与危险</li></ul>",
